---
import CalendlyButton from "./CalendlyButton.astro";
---

<footer id="site-footer" class="mt-24 pb-10 max-md:mt-14 max-md:pb-0">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 max-md:px-0">
    <div
      class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem]  bg-cover bg-center max-md:rounded-none"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/35 backdrop-blur-[1px]"></div>

      <div class="relative px-6 pt-20 pb-8 md:px-10 md:pt-28 max-md:px-0 max-md:pt-12 max-md:pb-0">
        <a
          href="#site-top"
          class="footer-scroll-link"
          aria-label="Retour en haut de page"
        >
          ↑
        </a>

        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 text-center max-md:max-w-none">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold leading-relaxed text-[var(--brown-deep)] max-md:text-xl">
            Prendre soin de soi, c’est se donner la possibilité de vivre plus aligné et plus serein.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 soft-card rounded-t-[2.5rem] rounded-b-none p-8 md:p-10 max-md:mt-10 max-md:rounded-none max-md:p-4">
          <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_0.8fr_0.9fr] max-md:grid-cols-2 max-md:gap-5">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 max-md:col-span-2 max-md:flex-row max-md:items-start max-md:gap-4">
              <img
                src="/images/sophro/moi-pont-plage.webp"
                alt="Alexandra Coirier, sophrologue à Loudéac"
                class="h-60 w-40 rounded-full object-cover shadow-lg max-md:h-28 max-md:w-20 max-md:flex-none"
              />

              <div class="min-w-0">
                <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brown-deep)] max-md:text-lg">
                  Alexandra Coirier
                </p>

                <p class="mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--brown-soft)] max-md:text-[0.65rem] max-md:tracking-[0.18em]">
                  Sophrologue à Loudéac
                </p>

                <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-[var(--text)] max-md:mt-3 max-md:text-sm">
                  J’accompagne les personnes qui traversent une période de stress,
                  d’anxiété, de fatigue, de surcharge mentale ou de transition de vie.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-6 max-md:mt-4">
                  <CalendlyButton
                    label="Prendre rendez-vous"
                    className="px-6 py-3 max-md:px-4 max-md:py-2 max-md:text-sm"
                    url="https://calendly.com/alexandracoirier-sophrologue/?hide_gdpr_banner=1&primary_color=9a6750&text_color=5e4a42&background_color=f8f2ef"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brown-deep)] max-md:text-base">
                Navigation
              </p>

              <nav class="mt-5 grid gap-3 text-[var(--text)] max-md:mt-3 max-md:gap-2">
                <a href="/" class="footer-link">Accueil</a>
                <a href="/a-quoi-s-attendre" class="footer-link">À quoi s’attendre</a>
                <a href="/accompagnement" class="footer-link">Accompagnements</a>
                <a href="/mon-approche" class="footer-link">Mon approche</a>
                <a href="/qui-suis-je" class="footer-link">Qui suis-je ?</a>
                <a href="/faq" class="footer-link">FAQ</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="footer-link">Contact</a>
              </nav>
            </div>

            <div>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brown-deep)] max-md:text-base">
                Informations
              </p>

              <div class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-[var(--text)] max-md:mt-3 max-md:space-y-2">
                <p>
                  <a href="tel:+33781528517" class="footer-link">
                    07 81 52 85 17
                  </a>
                </p>

                <p>
                  <a
                    href="mailto:contact@alexandracoirier-sophrologue.fr"
                    class="footer-link break-all"
                  >
                    contact@alexandracoirier-sophrologue.fr
                  </a>
                </p>

                <p>
                  26 Rue du Dr Robin<br />
                  22600 Loudéac
                </p>
              </div>

              <nav class="mt-6 grid gap-3 text-sm max-md:mt-4 max-md:gap-2">
                <a href="/mentions-legales" class="footer-link">Mentions légales</a>
                <a href="/politique-confidentialite" class="footer-link">Confidentialité</a>
                <a href="/politique-cookies" class="footer-link">Cookies</a>
              </nav>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="-mt-1 rounded-b-[2.5rem] bg-[var(--brown-deep)]/85 px-6 py-5 md:px-10 max-md:rounded-none max-md:px-4 max-md:py-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-white/90 max-md:text-center">
            <p class="max-md:text-xs">
              © 2025 Alexandra Coirier – Sophrologue à Loudéac • Tous droits réservés
            </p>

            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a
                href="https://www.facebook.com/p/Alexandra-Coirier-Sophrologue-100072807305535/"
                class="footer-social"
                aria-label="Facebook"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                f
              </a>

              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/alexandracoirier_sophrologie/"
                class="footer-social"
                aria-label="Instagram"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                ◎
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer-link {
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 220ms ease, transform 220ms ease;
  }

  .footer-link:hover {
    color: var(--brown-deep);
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .footer-social {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 220ms ease, background 220ms ease;
  }

  .footer-social:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  }

  .footer-scroll-link {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2rem;
    right: 2rem;
    z-index: 20;
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: var(--brown-soft);
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(94, 74, 66, 0.25);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    #site-footer {
      width: 100%;
    }

    #site-footer .soft-card {
      border-left: 0;
      border-right: 0;
    }

    #site-footer p,
    #site-footer a {
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .footer-scroll-link {
      top: 1rem;
      right: 1rem;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .footer-social {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
    }
  }
</style>